                        <li class="m-lg-2"><a href="https://api.vapor.codes" target="_blank" class="dropdown-item"><div class="nav-dropdown-container d-flex"><span class="vapor-icon icon-dataflow-03" aria-hidden="true"></span><div class="ms-3"><div class="nav-dropdown-container-title">API Docs</div><div class="nav-dropdown-container-caption d-none d-lg-block">Reference documentation for Vapor</div></div></div></a></li>
