                        <div class="col-lg blog-tags pt-4 pt-lg-0 d-flex align-items-center"><ul class="mx-auto mx-lg-0 flex-wrap"><li class="my-1"><a href="#">Vapor</a></li><li class="my-1"><a href="#">Framework</a></li></ul></div>
